🧠 1) Loops (beyond basics)
🔹 Iteration patterns
Element iteration: for x in arr
Index + value: for i, x in enumerate(arr)
Windowed iteration: process arr[i-k:i] efficiently (see sliding window)
🔹 Early exit (performance)
Stop as soon as goal is met:
